item.title: CVE-2023-0033|2024-08-02T04:54:32.593Z -- unknown -- pdf%20viewer
item.description: The PDF Viewer WordPress plugin before 1.0.0 does not validate and escape one of its shortcode attributes, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attack.
